[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0245","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0245.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0686","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server HP-UX 长URL 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server (NES) 在处理超长 URL 时存在拒绝服务漏洞。攻击者无需身份认证即可向运行在 HP-UX 平台上的 HP Virtual Vault (VVOS) 系统中的 NES 服务器发送特制超长 URL 请求，导致服务器进程崩溃或资源耗尽，无法正常响应合法用户请求。该漏洞影响 HP Virtual Vault 操作系统上部署的 Netscape Enterprise Server 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。厂商已发布安全补丁修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0686"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.783","remediation":"Netscape Enterprise Server 已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx）。如无法迁移，可在反向代理或防火墙层面限制传入 URL 长度不超过 4096 字节，并配置访问控制列表仅允许可信 IP 访问管理端口，以降低拒绝服务攻击风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-046.shtml","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9906-098","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/985d46f062894917f05cdf3d64399a32839d12b7/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0686.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0686","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0686.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/5d448b12fda744aa8491fddc8705260f2b4289f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0686.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cd61cf4d5a67ce31725304e4ddf8e4e21c23dbc3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mrj2-v329-4cm9/GHSA-mrj2-v329-4cm9.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0686.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0245.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0245.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1808","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1808.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1241","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 在安全级别设置为\"中\"以下时，存在 ActiveX 控件远程代码执行漏洞。远程攻击者可通过构造恶意网页，利用 FileSystemObject ActiveX 对象执行任意命令，导致系统被完全控制。该漏洞影响所有将 IE 安全级别设置为\"中\"以下的 Windows 系统版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1241"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:01.150","remediation":"将 Internet Explorer 安全级别设置为「中」或更高（控制面板 → Internet 选项 → 安全 → Internet 区域 → 自定义级别）；禁用「对未标记为可安全执行脚本的 ActiveX 控件进行初始化和脚本化」；在注册表中设置 FileSystemObject 控件的 kill bit (CLSID: 0D43FE01-F093-11CF-8940-00A0C9054228)，或运行 Microsoft 提供的 FSO 安全更新。建议升级到现代浏览器（如 Edge/Chrome）以彻底规避此风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://oliver.efri.hr/~crv/security/bugs/NT/activex4.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2173"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1808.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1083","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1083.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1367","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.0 受限网站凭据缓存泄漏漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.0 在访问未使用标准缓存控制的网站时，无法正确重置用户名/密码缓存，导致同一系统上的其他用户可通过浏览器的缓存数据访问受限网站。该漏洞利用条件为攻击者需与目标用户共用同一系统，属于本地信息泄露漏洞，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1367"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:17.353","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 6.0 或更高版本，或改用现代浏览器（如 Edge/Chrome/Firefox）。使用 IE 时启用隐私浏览模式，避免在共享系统中保存网站密码，使用后手动清除凭据缓存。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.pcworld.com/news/article/0%2Caid%2C10842%2C00.asp","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1367.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1367","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1367.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1367.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w6vf-5ccm-v948/GHSA-w6vf-5ccm-v948.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1367.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000629.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/b929f4524cd5f55e84af4c34d9f33ee2512d5d4a/1999.tsv","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1083.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1005","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1005.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1195","title":"NAI VirusScan NT 病毒定义更新验证缺失漏洞","description":"NAI VirusScan NT 4.0.2 在通过 FTP 更新病毒定义文件 scan.dat 时存在更新验证缺陷。当更新过程实际失败时，软件仍错误地报告更新成功，导致系统管理员误认为病毒库已正确更新至最新版本。攻击者可利用此漏洞通过中间人攻击或篡改 FTP 服务器响应，使目标系统无法获取最新的病毒定义，从而降低对恶意软件的检测能力，增加系统被感染的风险。该漏洞影响 NAI VirusScan NT 4.0.2，CVSS 评分 5.1，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1195"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:55.253","remediation":"升级至 Network Associates VirusScan NT 4.0.3a，该版本已修复此问题。升级前建议先卸载或禁用 4.0.2 版本以避免服务无法正常停止。临时缓解措施：手动停止 VirusScan 引擎进程，等待数秒后手动复制病毒定义文件至 VirusScan NT 目录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92588169005196&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92587579032534&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/169","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1195.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1195","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1195.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f9199c6ea2112c9d2536a126688b640a45f0982a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1195.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pm4g-gv9m-qf7v/GHSA-pm4g-gv9m-qf7v.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/169/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1195.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/dd9f81e9fd85457bf78c55783cb6a31e9af71d63/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1005.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0938","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0938.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1097","title":"Microsoft NetMeeting 剪贴板信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft NetMeeting 2.1 存在信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在聊天窗口为空时发送 CTRL-C 组合键，读取另一客户端剪贴板中的敏感内容。该漏洞源于 NetMeeting 对剪贴板访问权限控制不足，导致攻击者可跨会话获取用户复制到剪贴板的密码、文件路径等私密信息，影响使用 NetMeeting 2.1 版本的 Windows 系统，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1097"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:42.933","remediation":"升级到 Microsoft NetMeeting 2.2 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 2.2 版中得到修复。如无法升级，在召开会议时避免使用聊天窗口，或在空白聊天框中按下 Ctrl-C 前先清空本地剪贴板。鉴于 NetMeeting 已被 Microsoft 正式停止支持并从 Windows 中移除，建议迁移至 Microsoft Teams 或 Skype for Business 等受支持的现代协作工具。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92586457816446&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2187","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1097.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1097","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1097.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c1321b1a6b0cb3a4c18f791e2c8443742c0cb0b0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1097.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mqf5-wgx4-qfwq/GHSA-mqf5-wgx4-qfwq.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88089/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1097.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--c0541269-d818-4679-85ab-e9c9f0b37426.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0938.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0861","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0861.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1012","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":10240,\"inputTokens\":543,\"outputTokens\":19,\"totalTokens\":10802}}","description":"tags.<value>Lotus Domino 4.6.1 的 SMTP 邮件服务组件在处理 SMTP 命令时存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标服务器发送超长字符串数据触发缓冲区处理异常，导致邮件服务进程崩溃或系统重启，造成邮件服务中断。该漏洞影响运行在 AS/400 及其他操作系统上的 Domino 4.6.1 版本，CVSS 评分为 5.0，危害等级为中等。攻击者可通过 Telnet 或脚本工具直接构造恶意 SMTP 请求进行利用，造成拒绝服务攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1012"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.237","remediation":"建议升级到 IBM Domino 4.6.2 或更高版本，该版本已修复 SMTP 组件对超长字符串输入缺乏边界检查导致的拒绝服务漏洞。如暂无法升级，应在 AS/400 防火墙或网关层对 SMTP 服务（TCP 25 端口）配置访问控制列表，仅允许可信来源 IP 访问，并在 Domino 配置文档中启用 SMTP 命令长度限制，通过设置 `SMTPMaxCommandLength` 参数来拦截超长 SMTP 命令，防止攻击者利用长字符串导致邮件服务崩溃。同时监控 Domino SMTP 任务日志，发现异常长连接请求时立即阻断。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13527","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/173","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/9a9b6476a3f4a52ffa21ec6ed80d737eb0fc242b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1012.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1012","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1012.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a6f1dc1488b4a75cccf07339e6a0f0ab45fc38ad/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1012.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/424512debdca84cc53ffa1fb3810a74f7b1905a5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r57w-9jx6-rq8c/GHSA-r57w-9jx6-rq8c.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/173/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1012.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000624.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ec3d87f4-fde6-4813-a971-0de566252091.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/54a49c35dfc49a19cf6de178ce37c0c006f4fb21/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0861.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-2000","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-2000.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1553","title":"Xcmail Xcmail 0.99.6 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"XCmail 0.99.6 邮件客户端在启用自动引用功能时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过发送超长邮件主题行触发栈缓冲区溢出，进而在受害者机器上以当前用户权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 XCmail 0.99.6 版本，攻击者需诱导受害者打开或预览包含超长主题的邮件即可触发，无需用户交互即可实现远程代码执行，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级为严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1553"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:42.237","remediation":"升级 XCmail 至官方已修复该缓冲区溢出问题的后续版本（0.99.7 及以上，或迁移至维护中的替代邮件客户端）。在无法立即升级时，关闭 XCmail 的 autoquote 自动引用功能，并避免打开来自不可信来源的含超长主题行的邮件作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/12730","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/311","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1859","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19249","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/68b3c685b96421db99cac9beb9d7bc8a6314be79/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1553.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1553","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1553.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/36499b7630ab4a32d11ab7c901b4c87271211bec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1553.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/645f3b3aab113438413618cef41319453f39d643/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9v58-477m-vwrq/GHSA-9v58-477m-vwrq.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1553.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--534d0215-1212-4123-a229-10e0d9591039.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/70290debf97c1057397e6f7c8c733dec0658bf76/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-2000.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1103","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1103.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1418","title":"ICQ ICQ 99a Web 服务器信息泄露漏洞","description":"ICQ 99a 的 Web 服务器组件（build 1701）在启用 \"Active Homepage\" 功能时存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的文件访问请求，根据服务器返回的差异响应（文件存在时返回 \"404 Forbidden\"，文件不存在时返回 \"404 not found\"）来枚举服务器上的文件是否存在。该漏洞影响 ICQ 99a 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等，攻击者无需认证即可利用此漏洞探测服务器敏感文件路径，为进一步攻击收集信息。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1418"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:23.923","remediation":"升级 ICQ 至 2000 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本修复。如无法升级，在 ICQ 设置中关闭\"Active Homepage\"（活动主页）功能以消除信息泄露风险。鉴于 ICQ 服务已于 2024 年 6 月 26 日正式停止运营，建议彻底停用 ICQ 并迁移至其他即时通讯软件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13508","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/246","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1418.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1418","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1418.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1418.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/icq_vulns.nasl","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/icq_installed.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1418.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/246/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1103.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0570","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0570.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0807","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9121,\"outputTokens\":17,\"totalTokens\":10802}}","description":"Netscape Directory Server 在安装过程中会将包含敏感信息（如管理员口令、配置凭据等）的文件以不当权限保留在本地文件系统中，该文件可被本地普通用户直接读取。此漏洞影响在本地安装 Netscape Directory Server 的系统，攻击条件为攻击者需拥有目标主机的本地登录权限或本地文件读取权限。本地用户通过访问安装过程遗留的敏感文件即可获取凭据等关键信息，进而可能提升权限或进一步攻击目录服务，造成信息泄露与潜在的服务沦陷风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0807"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.883","remediation":"安装完成后立即删除安装过程中生成的临时文件（如 install.log、setup.ini），并将安装目录权限设置为 750（仅管理员可读写执行），防止本地用户访问敏感配置信息。建议升级至 Red Hat Directory Server 或 389 Directory Server 等仍在维护的替代产品。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0807","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1ce36d0de2f3ddd1d56c222c398df994c8c331b1/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0807.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0807","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0807.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f581b54f28a314b57ac171b83d3b2d21db7414a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0807.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/11845a9fe6e6b4d82150d9fd8a4257b88a244a45/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wq96-x226-v8pj/GHSA-wq96-x226-v8pj.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0807.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88045/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000620.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--7f943c92-5f2b-46a9-a805-848982ba4e64.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0570.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0481","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0481.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0764","title":"NetBSD ARP 协议实现安全缺陷（ARP 欺骗）","description":"NetBSD 操作系统的 ARP 协议实现存在安全缺陷，系统在接收到 ARP 数据包时未对静态 ARP 条目进行有效保护。攻击者只要处于同一局域网二层广播域中，即可通过构造并发送伪造的 ARP 数据包（ARP 欺骗/ARP 毒化），使内核用攻击者提供的 MAC 地址覆盖管理员预先手动配置的静态 ARP 映射。该漏洞影响运行 NetBSD 且配置了静态 ARP 条目的主机，攻击无需身份认证，仅需网络可达。利用成功后，攻击者可实施中间人攻击、流量劫持或拒绝服务，进而监听或篡改目标主机与其他设备之间的通信।","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0764"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:00.597","remediation":"升级 NetBSD 到 1.4 及以上版本或应用特定安全补丁：https://ftp.NetBSD.org/pub/NetBSD/misc/security/patches/19990208-netstat，该补丁修复了 ARP 协议相关的内核内存访问控制问题。此外，如无法立即更新，可以通过 `chmod 400 /usr/sbin/netstat` 禁止非根用户访问 netstat 命令以缓解该 ARP 条目覆盖漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T06:12:45.574533404+00:00","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6539","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e244b55bdff85b2483c0e6a7cecd12f8bee0df6e/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0764.json","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0764"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0481.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0480","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0480.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0763","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9111,\"outputTokens\":20,\"totalTokens\":10795}}","description":"CVE-1999-0763 是 NetBSD 操作系统在多宿主主机（即配备多个网络接口并连接不同网络的主机）上存在的 ARP 缓存处理缺陷。攻击者可向其中一个网络发送特制的 ARP 数据包，由于系统未能正确隔离不同网络接口上的 ARP 信息，该数据包会被错误地用于修改另一个相连网络的 ARP 缓存条目，从而实施 ARP 欺骗或中间人攻击。该漏洞影响运行 NetBSD 且配置为连接多个网络的多宿主主机，攻击条件为攻击者能够访问其中一个相连网络并向目标发送伪造的 ARP 报文，利用方式是通过跨网络的 ARP 缓存污染实现流量劫持或会话拦截。CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级为中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0763"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:00.467","remediation":"升级到 NetBSD 1.4 及以上版本，或从 ftp://ftp.NetBSD.ORG/pub/NetBSD/misc/security/patches/19990505-arp 获取并应用内核补丁。如无法升级，可在各网络接口上使用 arp -s 添加静态 ARP 条目并配合防火墙规则限制 ARP 流量来源，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6540","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e268305fd8644994d337819e469d1f89bafde833/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0763.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0763","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0763.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0ea6b1a1298433599abdd2a4c6b6ce9f09476665/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0763.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d9ad03f9df46533ce9229f9da6bbf66bd77a3f4f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3q2q-j727-g75q/GHSA-3q2q-j727-g75q.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0763.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000619.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/39b9df25423a93bff6d75a66d90cb36757da74c2/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0480.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0159","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0159.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0487","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer DHTML Edit ActiveX 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 中的 DHTML Edit ActiveX 控件存在任意文件读取漏洞。远程攻击者可通过构造恶意网页，诱使用户在 IE 浏览器中访问，利用该 ActiveX 控件的跨帧访问特性读取目标系统上的任意文件内容。该漏洞影响 Internet Explorer 4 和 5 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可实施攻击，危害用户隐私安全。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0487"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:30.130","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 6 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 IE 5.5 SP2 及后续版本中修复。如无法升级，可通过注册表设置 Kill Bit 禁用 DHTML Edit ActiveX 控件（CLSID: {2D360201-FFF5-11D1-8D03-00A0C959BC0A}），在 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\ActiveX Compatibility 下创建对应 CLSID 项并将 Compatibility Flags 设为 0x400。建议迁移至现代浏览器（如 Edge/Chrome/Firefox）以彻底规避风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-011","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19094","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/58a0ea900decdd7e971b95fcaa99234de5a5df5e/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0487.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0487","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0487.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/dabf5b9888e8885cf125c5729901a7ad84d00092/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0487.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-79cg-j8cc-gwm8/GHSA-79cg-j8cc-gwm8.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0487.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/bibliotxt/bibliotxt/blob/07bb3ac8e74e6f78514faabae1ce10b662cf48a1/zines/trenchcoat-diaries/tcpaper2.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/akabe1/windows_exploit_dowser/blob/11b24e36173cd382721db28581e575faf687d06b/cve_from_exploitdb_website.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0159.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0159.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0007","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0007.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0194","title":"UNIX in.comsat 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"in.comsat（Unix 邮件通知服务）存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标主机的 comsat 服务（UDP 512 端口）发送特制的伪造消息数据包，触发服务生成大量告警通知并消耗系统资源，导致目标主机拒绝服务。受影响的系统包括各类 Unix 衍生系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等问题。厂商已发布安全补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0194"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:53.103","remediation":"在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释或删除 comsat 行并重启 inetd 服务以禁用该服务；或在防火墙上封禁外部对 UDP 512 端口的访问。如需保留功能，请升级操作系统至厂商已发布修复补丁的最新版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0194"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0007.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0303","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0303.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0711","title":"Oracle 8.x Intelligent Agent oratclsh 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Oracle 8.x Unix版智能代理中的oratclsh解释器存在权限提升漏洞。该解释器设置了SUID位，导致本地攻击者可以root用户身份执行任意Tcl命令，从而完全控制目标系统。攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限才能利用此漏洞，CVSS评分4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0711"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:53.820","remediation":"立即从 Oracle Metalink（http://www.oracle.com/support/elec_sup）下载并运行 setuid_patch.sh 脚本，该脚本会移除 oratclsh 可执行文件并清除所有非必要 Oracle 二进制文件的 setuid 权限位。如无法获取补丁，可手动执行 `chmod -s $ORACLE_HOME/bin/oratclsh` 移除 setuid 位，或直接删除 oratclsh 文件。升级到 Oracle 8.0.6 或 8.1.6 及以上版本可彻底修复此问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92609807906778&w=2","http://marc.info/?t=92550157100002&w=2&r=1","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19125","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64d76d92cfbd9c4de4a352a59a2e52cadebc3afd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0711.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0711","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0711.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/89b3a1c34ab26afed5cfe4fc54b61cecbf09d3c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0711.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1dbd44058e428445290bfb1f6fc6ecc0addbfd35/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4pfh-v638-25xp/GHSA-4pfh-v638-25xp.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0711.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d1c0adaa-8a04-48dc-8913-b4362b415c10.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0303.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0305","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0305.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0712","title":"Caldera Open Administration System 敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"Caldera Open Administration System (COAS) 存在权限配置不当漏洞，导致系统 /etc/shadow 密码文件被设置为全局可读。攻击者可通过本地访问读取该文件，获取系统所有用户的密码哈希值，进而通过离线破解获得明文密码。该漏洞影响 Caldera 相关操作系统版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，利用前提为攻击者已获得本地访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0712"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:53.950","remediation":"立即升级到受支持的现代 Linux 发行版（如 SUSE Linux Enterprise 或 OpenSUSE），Caldera OpenLinux 及 COAS 已停止维护多年，不再提供安全更新。如无法升级，可手动执行 `chmod 600 /etc/shadow` 确保 shadow 文件仅 root 可读，并移除 COAS 的 setuid 二进制文件或卸载 COAS 软件包以消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0712","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6df16fc0c02ccadd2d0fbb0029e3db345d75f1c8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0712.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0712","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0712.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ec31d5593e31331ed2058e001803e087d65aa416/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0712.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7h3x-fvwr-j2mc/GHSA-7h3x-fvwr-j2mc.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0712.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/137/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000617.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5fa43793-28e7-4c55-8c2b-61efcb2270d5.json","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0305.toml"}]